Package it.polimi.ingsw.client.view

Class Gui

java.lang.Object
it.polimi.ingsw.client.view.UI
it.polimi.ingsw.client.view.Gui
public class Gui
extends UI
Gui class representing Graphical User Interface part of the project that can be used as an alternative to CLI for this reason the both inherit from UI abstract class. It contains several overloading methods whose task consists in submitting message render to GUIApp main thread.
